printBigrams

public void printBigrams(PrintWriter output,
                         BigramExtractor.SignificanceTest test,
                         int minOccurrencePerToken)
Prints all of the known bigrams, where each token in the bigram must occur at least the number of specified time.

Parameters:
output - the writer where all the bigrams should be printed
test - the significant test to use in rating the statistical correlation of two tokens
minOccurrencePerToken - the minimum number of times each token in a bigram must occur for the bigram's score to be reported
